{"id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0001", "text": "[Construction](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0001", "source_slug": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester", "source_title": "Steward or accountant?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/rentmeester-of-rekenmeester.html", "source_date": "2025-09-23", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "bouw", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 1, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 1}}
{"id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0002", "text": "[Leontien de Waal](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/authors/leontien-de-waal/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0002", "source_slug": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester", "source_title": "Steward or accountant?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/rentmeester-of-rekenmeester.html", "source_date": "2025-09-23", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "bouw", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 2}}
{"id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0003", "text": "The construction and real estate sector is full of idealists. People who work with conviction on sustainable, nature-inclusive and climate-adaptive living environments. Stewardship focused on nature is the moral compass here. But skeptics are stirring.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0003", "source_slug": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester", "source_title": "Steward or accountant?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/rentmeester-of-rekenmeester.html", "source_date": "2025-09-23", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "bouw", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 3}}
{"id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0004", "text": "They believe that we have gone too far in terms of sustainability requirements in the built environment, that biodiversity is something for Sundays and that everything could do with an ounce less. In a time of rising costs and scarcity of space and labor, their credo is: fewer rules and being frugal.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0004", "source_slug": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester", "source_title": "Steward or accountant?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/rentmeester-of-rekenmeester.html", "source_date": "2025-09-23", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "bouw", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 4}}
{"id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0005", "text": "Between these extremes the foundation is in danger of sinking. Because without a shared language about value, we continue to bombard each other with beliefs. One with the moral obligation to liveability, the other with the requirement of affordability.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0005", "source_slug": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester", "source_title": "Steward or accountant?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/rentmeester-of-rekenmeester.html", "source_date": "2025-09-23", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "bouw", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 5}}
{"id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0006", "text": "> “It is time for the steward to also become an accountant, to make broad value visible and financially relevant.”", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0006", "source_slug": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester", "source_title": "Steward or accountant?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/rentmeester-of-rekenmeester.html", "source_date": "2025-09-23", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "bouw", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 6}}
{"id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0007", "text": "That is why it is time for the steward to also become an accountant. Not to flatten nature into an Excel line, but to make broad value visible and financially relevant. Because who substantiates sustainability, makes it defensible.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0007", "source_slug": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester", "source_title": "Steward or accountant?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/rentmeester-of-rekenmeester.html", "source_date": "2025-09-23", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "bouw", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 7}}
{"id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0008", "text": "The damage to nature is real. Previous research by ABN AMRO and the Impact Institute shows that the Dutch economy causes almost 40 billion euros in damage to biodiversity every year. More than 70 percent of this takes place abroad, often through the use of materials in the chain. Construction and real estate also contribute, both directly and indirectly. We just don't calculate it yet.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0008", "source_slug": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester", "source_title": "Steward or accountant?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/rentmeester-of-rekenmeester.html", "source_date": "2025-09-23", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "bouw", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 8}}
{"id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0009", "text": "And that is not only ecologically unsustainable, it is also economically stupid. As long as we do not include the costs and benefits of quality of life, health or climate adaptation, we focus on the short term. Heat islands, flooding and reduced mental health will soon present us with the bill through healthcare costs, recovery costs and reduced productivity.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0009", "source_slug": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester", "source_title": "Steward or accountant?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/rentmeester-of-rekenmeester.html", "source_date": "2025-09-23", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "bouw", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 9}}
{"id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0010", "text": "To make truly impactful choices, we need to talk more in the language of financial values. Which low-CO₂ materials contribute not only to emission reductions, but also to more robust buildings with lower operating costs? How do shade and coolness from mature trees affect real estate returns? Making this visible opens up new business cases.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0010", "source_slug": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester", "source_title": "Steward or accountant?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/rentmeester-of-rekenmeester.html", "source_date": "2025-09-23", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "bouw", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 10, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 10}}
{"id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0011", "text": "> “To make impactful choices, we need to talk more in the language of financial values.”", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0011", "source_slug": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester", "source_title": "Steward or accountant?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/rentmeester-of-rekenmeester.html", "source_date": "2025-09-23", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "bouw", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 11, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 11}}
{"id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0012", "text": "True Pricing (the price including social costs) provides an explanation for this. Just like the DuPa 2.0, the sustainability section in the valuation report, which translates sustainability aspects into the market value of buildings. Anyone who really wants to build in a future-proof manner must be a steward and an accountant. Now is the time to unite those two roles.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0012", "source_slug": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester", "source_title": "Steward or accountant?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/rentmeester-of-rekenmeester.html", "source_date": "2025-09-23", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "bouw", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 12, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 12}}
{"id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0013", "text": "This column previously appeared in Cobouw on September 19, 2025", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0013", "source_slug": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester", "source_title": "Steward or accountant?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/rentmeester-of-rekenmeester.html", "source_date": "2025-09-23", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "bouw", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 13, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 13}}
{"id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0014", "text": "[Leontien de Waal](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/authors/leontien-de-waal.html) is a Construction sector banker. She follows the most important trends and developments in the built environment. She brings her experience and network, supplemented with knowledge from the Master City Developer (area development) course, to ABN AMRO clients.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0014", "source_slug": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester", "source_title": "Steward or accountant?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/rentmeester-of-rekenmeester.html", "source_date": "2025-09-23", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "bouw", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 14, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 14}}
{"id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0015", "text": "The Dutch construction sector has been one of the best performing sectors in recent years, despite several challenges facing the sector. Examples are the nitrogen dossier, the significant price increases for energy and building materials and also the personnel shortages. Driven by trends, innovations and legislation and regulations, the relevance of themes such as sustainability and environmental impact is growing and the sector is looking for a new balance.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester__a2-late-chunking__0015", "source_slug": "rentmeester-of-rekenmeester", "source_title": "Steward or accountant?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/bouw/rentmeester-of-rekenmeester.html", "source_date": "2025-09-23", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "bouw", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 15, "n_chunks_total": 27, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 15}}
